'
' Command
'  -Wb Spline

Screen Open 0,320,256,8,0
Flash Off : Curs Off : Cls 0 : Ink 2
'
Gr Writing 2
While Mouse Key<>1 : Wend 
X0=X Screen(X Mouse)
Y0=Y Screen(Y Mouse)
'
While Mouse Key=1
   X1=X Screen(X Mouse)
   Y1=Y Screen(Y Mouse)
   Draw X0,Y0 To X1,Y1
   While X1+Y1=X Screen(X Mouse)+Y Screen(Y Mouse) : Wend 
   Draw X0,Y0 To X1,Y1
Wend 
'
While Mouse Key=0
   X2=X Screen(X Mouse)
   Y2=Y Screen(Y Mouse)
   Wb Spline X0,Y0 To X2,Y2 To X1,Y1,12
   Wait Vbl 
   Wb Spline X0,Y0 To X2,Y2 To X1,Y1,12
Wend 
'
Gr Writing 1
Ink 5 : Wb Spline X0,Y0 To X2,Y2 To X1,Y1,12
